addInAllApiCall(bytes32).details: Stores the id return by the oraclize query.  Maintains record of all the Ids return by oraclize query.

params.myid: Id return by the oraclize query.

changeCurrencyAssetBaseMin(bytes4,uint25.details: Changes base minimum of a given currency asset.

changeCurrencyAssetVarMin(bytes4,uint256.details: changes variable minimum of a given currency asset.

changeInvestmentAssetHoldingPerc(bytes4,.details: Changes the investment asset Holding percentage of a given currency.

changeNotariseAddress(address).details: Changes address allowed to post MCR.

getApiCallDetails(bytes32).details: Get Details of Oraclize API when given Oraclize Id.

params.myid: ID return by the oraclize query.

getApiCallDetails(bytes32).return: _typeof ype of the query for which oraclize  call is made.("proposal","quote","quotation" etc.)

getApiCallIndex(uint256).details: Gets ID return by the oraclize query of a given index.
getApiCallIndex(uint256).return: myid ID return by the oraclize query.

getApiIdTypeOf(bytes32).details: Gets type of oraclize query for a given Oraclize Query ID.

params.myid: Oraclize Query ID identifying the query for which the result is being received.

getApiIdTypeOf(bytes32).return: _typeof It could be of type "quote","quotation","cover","claim" etc.

getCAAvgRate(bytes4).details: to get the average rate of currency rate

getCurrenciesByIndex(uint256).details: Gets All currency for a given index.

getCurrencyAssetBaseMin(bytes4).details: Gets base minimum of  a given currency asset.

getCurrencyAssetVarBase(bytes4).details: Gets currency asset details for a given currency.

getCurrencyAssetVarMin(bytes4).details: Gets minimum variable value for currency asset.

getDateAddOfAPI(bytes32).details: Gets the Timestamp of a oracalize call.

getDateUpdOfAPI(bytes32).details: Gets the Timestamp at which result of oracalize call is received.

getIAAvgRate(bytes4).details: to get the average rate of investment rate

getIARankDetailsByDate(uint64).details: Gets investment asset rank details by given date.

getIdOfApiId(bytes32).details: Gets ID associated to oraclize query for a given Oraclize Query ID.

params.myid: Oraclize Query ID identifying the query for which the result is being received.

getIdOfApiId(bytes32).return: id1 It could be the ID of "proposal","quotation","cover","claim" etc.

getInvestmentAssetDetails(bytes4).details: Gets investment asset details of a given currency

getInvestmentAssetHoldingPerc(bytes4).details: Gets investment asset maximum and minimum holding percentage of a given currency.

getInvestmentAssetMaxHoldingPerc(bytes4).details: Gets investment asset maximum holding percentage of a given currency.

getInvestmentAssetMinHoldingPerc(bytes4).details: Gets investment asset minimum holding percentage of a given currency.

getInvestmentAssetStatus(bytes4).details: Gets investment asset active Status of a given currency.

getInvestmentCurrencyByIndex(uint256).details: Gets investment currency for a given index.

getLastMCR().details: Gets the details of last added MCR.
getLastMCR().return: mcrPercx100 Total Minimum Capital Requirement percentage of that month of year(multiplied by 100).vFull Total Pool fund value in Ether used in the last full daily calculation.

getLastMCRDate().details: Gets last Minimum Capital Requirement in Ether.

getLastMCREther().details: Gets last Ether price of Capital Model

getLastMCRPerc().details: Gets last Minimum Capital Requirement percentage of Capital Model

getLastVfull().details: Gets Pool fund value in Ether used in the last full daily calculation from the Capital model.

getMCRDataLength().details: Gets the total number of times MCR calculation has been made.

getTokenPriceDetails(bytes4).details: Gets details for token price calculation.

getUintParameters(bytes8).details: Gets Uint Parameters of a code
getUintParameters(bytes8).return: string value of the codeassociated amount (time or perc or value) to the code

isnotarise(address).details: Checks whether a given address can notaise MCR data or not.
isnotarise(address).return: res Returns 0 if address is not authorized, else 1.

params.vf: Pool fund value in Ether used in the last full daily calculation from the Capital model.

saveApiDetails(bytes32,bytes4,uint256).details: Saves the details of the Oraclize API.

params._typeof: type of the query for which oraclize call is made.
params.id: ID of the proposal,quote,cover etc. for which oraclize call is made
params.myid: Id return by the oraclize query.

setCapReached(uint256).details: to set the maximum cap allowed

setLastLiquidityTradeTrigger().details: to get the time for the laste liquidity trade trigger

updateCAAvgRate(bytes4,uint256).details: Updates the 3 day average rate of a CA currency. To be replaced by MakerDao's on chain rates

params.rate: Average exchange rate X 100 (of last 3 days).

updateDateUpdOfAPI(bytes32).details: Updates the Timestamp at which result of oracalize call is received.

updateIAAvgRate(bytes4,uint256).details: Updates the 3 day average rate of a IA currency. To be replaced by MakerDao's on chain rates

params.rate: Average exchange rate X 100 (of last 3 days).

updateUintParameters(bytes8,uint256).details: Updates Uint Parameters of a code

params.code: whose details we want to update
